    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      DAY_OF_MONTH
      The day of month represented by an integer from 1 to 31 in the usual manner.
      DAY_OF_WEEK
      The day of week represented by an integer from 0 to 6; 0 is Sunday, 1 is Monday, and so forth; thus 6 is Saturday.
      HOURS
      The hours represented by an integer from 0 to 23.
      MINUTES
      The minutes represented by an integer from 0 to 59 in the usual manner.
      MONTH
      The month represented by an integer from 0 to 11; 0 is January, 1 is February, and so forth; thus 11 is December.
      SECONDS
      The seconds represented by an integer from 0 to 61; the values 60 and 61 occur only for leap seconds.
      YEAR
      The year represented by an integer.
